    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>代码实现：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var express = require(&apos;express&apos;);</div><div class="line">var cookieParser = require(&apos;cookie-parser&apos;);</div><div class="line">var session = require(&apos;express-session&apos;);</div><div class="line">var MongoStore = require(&apos;connect-mongo&apos;)(session);</div><div class="line">var app = express();</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">app.use(cookieParser(&apos;sessiontest&apos;));</div><div class="line">app.use(session(&#123;</div><div class="line">    secret: &apos;sessiontest&apos;,</div><div class="line">    resave: true,</div><div class="line">    saveUninitalized: true,</div><div class="line">    store: new MongoStore(&#123;</div><div class="line">        url: &apos;mongodb://localhost:27017/sessionmongo&apos;</div><div class="line">    &#125;)</div><div class="line">&#125;));</div><div class="line">app.get(&apos;/login&apos;, function(req, res) &#123;</div><div class="line">    var user = &#123;</div><div class="line">        name: &quot;hester&quot;,</div><div class="line">        age: &quot;21&quot;</div><div class="line">    &#125;;</div><div class="line">    req.session.user = user;</div><div class="line">    res.redirect(&apos;/user&apos;);</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div><div class="line">app.listen(8080, function() &#123;</div><div class="line">    console.log(&quot;http://localhost:8080&quot;);</div><div class="line">&#125;);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p>引用模块：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var session = require(&apos;express-session&apos;);</div><div class="line">var MongoStore = require(&apos;connect-mongo&apos;)(session);</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>基本使用：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">app.use(session(&#123;</div><div class="line">    store: new MongoStore(&#123;</div><div class="line">        url: &apos;mongodb://localhost:27017/sessionmongo&apos;</div><div class="line">    &#125;)</div><div class="line">&#125;));</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>在页面创建session：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">var user = &#123;</div><div class="line">  name: &quot;hester&quot;,</div><div class="line">  age: &quot;21&quot;</div><div class="line">&#125;;</div><div class="line">req.session.user = user;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><blockquote><p>更多详细使用：<a href="https://github.com/jdesboeufs/connect-mongo" target="_blank" rel="external">https://github.com/jdesboeufs/connect-mongo</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
